00:21:10.895 --> 00:21:12.147
- Alto.

491
00:21:12.188 --> 00:21:13.648
* And who shall

492
00:21:13.690 --> 00:21:14.691
- Tenor.

493
00:21:14.733 --> 00:21:15.984
* The starry crown

