00:31:49.701 --> 00:31:52.245
- [Tiff] Very cute. bright.

741
00:31:52.287 --> 00:31:53.121
- Oh. it's bright.

742
00:31:53.163 --> 00:31:54.372
Mm-mm!
- No. no. no.

743
00:31:54.414 --> 00:31:55.123
- What do you think?

744
00:31:56.041 --> 00:31:58.168
- It's lovely. but...

745
00:31:58.209 --> 00:31:59.252
No. follow me.

