00:32:20.774 --> 00:32:22.692
So I think...

756
00:32:22.734 --> 00:32:23.860
(Tiff laughs)

757
00:32:23.902 --> 00:32:25.737
Okay.
(curtains rattling)

758
00:32:25.779 --> 00:32:27.739
Oh.
