00:32:29.407 --> 00:32:30.700
Try something else.
(curtains rattling)

761
00:32:30.742 --> 00:32:32.035
- [Lori] Oh my.

762
00:32:32.077 --> 00:32:34.496
- Oh my gosh.
looks very. very...

