00:51:05.065 --> 00:51:06.566
but one thing I can
control is how people

1147
00:51:06.608 --> 00:51:07.942
in the church see me.

1148
00:51:09.194 --> 00:51:11.154
- Maybe there's
something important

1149
00:51:11.196 --> 00:51:13.656
about sharing all
sides of yourself.

