You did great.

1292
00:57:46.216 --> 00:57:47.884
(Amanda laughs)

1293
00:57:47.926 --> 00:57:49.636
Good work! Wow!

1294
00:57:49.678 --> 00:57:50.762
You really got me.

1295
00:57:51.596 --> 00:57:53.098
(both laughing)

1296
00:57:53.139 --> 00:57:54.099
- I don't think I've
ever seen somebody look

