00:58:20.875 --> 00:58:23.420
- The three Ps?
- Mm-hmm.

1310
00:58:23.461 --> 00:58:25.964
Practice. practice. practice.

1311
00:58:27.799 --> 00:58:29.217
(Amanda sighs)

1312
00:58:29.259 --> 00:58:31.636
(gentle music)

