00:58:31.678 --> 00:58:33.930
(door clacks)
- All right.

1314
00:58:33.972 --> 00:58:36.933
Almost there.
(door thuds)

1315
00:58:40.979 --> 00:58:42.689
(Amanda sighs)

1316
00:58:42.731 --> 00:58:43.773
- It's incredible.

1317
00:58:44.649 --> 00:58:45.692
- Come on.

1318
00:58:45.734 --> 00:58:48.695
(Amanda chuckles)

1319
00:58:51.865 --> 00:58:55.910
So. this is what I
wanted to show you.

